[Name] DVB-Apps
[Summary] Video4Linux DVB device utilities.
[License] LGPL 2.1
[Description]The LinuxTV dvb-apps package contains some Linux DVB API applications and a set of utilities that both the developer and end user alike 
will find quite useful. Specifically, the utilities are geared towards the initial setup, testing, and operation of a DVB device.
[Homepage] http://www.linuxtv.org/wiki/index.php/LinuxTV_dvb-apps
